channel.title: God Wars Bosses? only need one more!
channel.description:
I have spent several hours trying to find all of the god wars bosses and i have got all of them but K'ril Tsutsaroth, Zamorak's general i would be willing to exchange models or something if anyone else needs the remaining 3 models Commander Zilyana, General Graardor, Kree'arra
If anyone has any models that have to do with god wars that would also be greatly appreciated!!
